rc=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />閻羅王同一眾牛頭馬面已經失守！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n在絕望中主角三人決定挺身而出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但由於地府缺乏武器，Ironman 情急之下只好報夢比pepper 叫佢燒件紙紮裝甲落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Thanos 則馬上趕造紙紮手套<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幸好的是黑寡婦本來就係佈景板所以影響不大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />究竟他們能否成功再一次阻止災難降臨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}